    <h1 class="post-hero-title">Getting Ready For Prom Season: A Family-Friendly, Faith-Focused Guide for the 417 Area</h1>
    <div class="post-meta-bar"><span>📅 March 11, 2026</span><span>✍️ Drew</span><span>⏱ 3 min read</span></div>
  </div>
